# committed as irreplaceable evidence for reports/decision_v7.md's real
# RTC transmission test. (Note: data/scenes/* not data/scenes/ -- a plain
# directory-level ignore blocks git from traversing into it at all, which
# makes a later "!" negation of a subdirectory silently not work.)
